        p Last Updated: August 28, 2019
        h4 Anatomy + Zoom Integration Overview    
        h5 Each time you complete a recorded meeting in Zoom, Anatomy will automatically:
        p.
            (1) Add the recording to a list for import. (2) Store the recording with Anatomy when imported. (3) Provide a page for recording playback (ffwd, rwd, speed adjustment) and video clip creation. (4) Enable note-taking and/or creation of a self-recorded introductory video linked directly to the original recording. (5) Generate a shareable & trackable URL for the imported recording + self recording + video clips + comments & likes.
        h4 Installation
        h5 How to Install the Anatomy Zoom app
        p.
            (1) Navigate to Zoom marketplace at https://marketplace.zoom.us (2) Search for Anatomy and click the app. (3) Click Sign in to Install and Login to your Zoom account. (4) Confirm the permissions the app requires and choose Allow. (5) You will see confirmation of Installation page.
        p.
            Anatomy is now installed on your Zoom account. Note: You or your Zoom admin would also need to enable Cloud recording downloads in https://zoom.us/account/setting?tab=recording of the primary account.


